{"tid":1832980,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦LHR轉機時間好短","createTime":"2020-01-21T14:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T22:36:31.000Z","uid":97811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a22c2510c9bb68f54759da11d9b8a4e57a77bd3c","tid":1832980,"uid":97811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"第一次去希斯路機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係倫敦轉機去布拉格得1.5小時<br />\nCheck過係T3轉T3<br />\n唔知趕唔趕得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗唔洗再過security check同拎行李?"},{"pid":"ae4fa780791f3e883a2ecf53497e7d31ae4a88b8","tid":1832980,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a22c2510c9bb68f54759da11d9b8a4e57a77bd3c","tid":1832980,"uid":97811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"第一次去希斯路機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係倫敦轉機去布拉格得1.5小時<br />\nCheck過係T3轉T3<br />\n唔知趕唔趕得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗唔洗再過security check同拎行李?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"得啦，好近，唔洗搞好多野。"},{"pid":"e3fa738d46fd1deecbe0ec452f4fa0479b4e331f","tid":1832980,"uid":101845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:20:35.000Z","msg":"我嚟緊T3 轉T2，三個鐘，唔知夠唔夠"},{"pid":"c647a8b9ce8524db2dfb886c64c04390eef7e91c","tid":1832980,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"你由邊度去LHR先,可以好煩的"},{"pid":"6e53069f5dbe3bd18d4c32b2f08cec674b7086b9","tid":1832980,"uid":45672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"如果你同一間航空公司嘅話<br />\n佢就行李自己幫你轉埋機冇問題<br />\n<br />\n我當年坐卡塔爾去英國坐BA去Iceland<br />\n<br />\n屌你落機到海關。拎行李。搞左個半鐘"},{"pid":"a9ce5a9f41aedcf2ce0b9d05557e0312d07ace99","tid":1832980,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:26:54.000Z","msg":"問題係你係LHR使唔使過custom<br />\n仲有, T5 與T1-3係唔同地方,要轉巴士,<br />\n如果冇記錯, e.g. HKG/LHR/PRG (神根歐洲) 係要係英國再過security check身check hand bags"},{"pid":"b20e46a8b0ae6dc261f50e8bb6c45abc940c4318","tid":1832980,"uid":97811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9ce5a9f41aedcf2ce0b9d05557e0312d07ace99","tid":1832980,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:26:54.000Z","msg":"問題係你係LHR使唔使過custom<br />\n仲有, T5 與T1-3係唔同地方,要轉巴士,<br />\n如果冇記錯, e.g. HKG/LHR/PRG (神根歐洲) 係要係英國再過security check身check hand bags"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"我HKG&gt;LHR呢程係virgin, LHR&gt;PRG係BA, T3落機T3上機<br />\n不過張機票係一齊買的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncheck嘢多人排隊咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1801106e27045be7a11cae9cb4fa801b42f724","tid":1832980,"uid":334812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"上次T5轉機 本身兩個鐘<br />\n但上一班delay 得返粒半 安檢人又多 最終要跑<br />\n<br />\n同Terminal 都好佢有啲閘口要坐列車<br />\n個度都要啲時間..."},{"pid":"4f49dacce6dbceea8a437f9f5636c6c0e117b786","tid":1832980,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b20e46a8b0ae6dc261f50e8bb6c45abc940c4318","tid":1832980,"uid":97811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9ce5a9f41aedcf2ce0b9d05557e0312d07ace99","tid":1832980,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:26:54.000Z","msg":"問題係你係LHR使唔使過custom<br />\n仲有, T5 與T1-3係唔同地方,要轉巴士,<br />\n如果冇記錯, e.g. HKG/LHR/PRG (神根歐洲) 係要係英國再過security check身check hand bags"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"我HKG&gt;LHR呢程係virgin, LHR&gt;PRG係BA, T3落機T3上機<br />\n不過張機票係一齊買的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncheck嘢多人排隊咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:58:13.000Z","msg":"行理記倉到PRG<br />\n人和手提要係T3過security 人多少,前面有冇人開喼令你等要睇天意。<br />\n唔記得使唔使過custom 如果係脫歐先後相信會亂 因為冇人有脫歐